Classes in org.cougaar.core.service.wp used by org.cougaar.core.service.wp
AddressEntry
          An AddressEntry represents a single entry in the white pages.
Application
          Deprecated. see new AddressEntry factory method
Callback
          A callback allowing asynchronous WhitePagesService interaction.
Cert
          A Cert holds the certification for an AddressEntry.
Request
          A request for the WhitePagesService.
Request.Bind
          Bind a new entry, or rebind an existing entry if the overwrite flag is false.
Request.Flush
          Modifies the local white pages cache to remove or refetch cached "getAll" or "list" data.
Request.Get
          Get the entry with the matching (name, type) fields.
Request.GetAll
          Get all entries associated with the given name.
Request.List
          List the name of all direct children with the given suffix.
Request.Unbind
          Destroy the binding for the specified entry.
Response
          A response from the WhitePagesService.
WhitePagesProtectionService.Wrapper
          Marker interface for a wrapper.
